Coventry University hosts a series of events across Nigeria for students looking to study abroad.  <img loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-1666453 aligncenter lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unnamed-66.png" alt="" width="451" height="236" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unnamed-66.png 451w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unnamed-66-320x167.jpg 320w" sizes="(max-width: 451px) 100vw, 451px" />Book your place at “An evening with Coventry University” and discover the opportunities that await you at an institution ranked top 30 in the world for its ratio of international students (QS World University Rankings 2022). You can meet the Coventry University team and alumni and learn more about the admissions process, scholarships and student support, alongside taking part in Q&As about student accommodation and visa applications. Meet us in: <img loading="lazy" class="wp-image-1666456 aligncenter lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unnamed-65.png" alt="" width="600" height="450" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unnamed-65.png 451w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unnamed-65-320x240.jpg 320w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unnamed-65-640x480.jpg 640w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" />  What to expect studying with Coventry University With 13,000 students from 130 countries studying at Coventry, the university is highly experienced in providing the right support, when you need it, so you can flourish in your new home. Coventry is home to a large Nigerian community, with around 800 students studying there currently. <img loading="lazy" class="wp-image-1666450 aligncenter lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unnamed-67.png" alt="" width="600" height="449" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unnamed-67.png 450w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unnamed-67-320x240.jpg 320w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unnamed-67-640x480.jpg 640w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" />Harry Tamunotonye, a graduate in MSc Global Healthcare Management, reflects on his experience at Coventry University: “Like many Nigerians, Coventry has become a home to me, and I now understand why it’s so popular. The university supports diversity, and I could thrive on all the resources they offer; I regret nothing. I received more support than I think I would have gotten in Nigeria, which really helped me in attaining a distinction.” Harry also received a grant, which was one of many bursaries and scholarships the university offers. Aerospace Systems Engineering BEng (Hons) student, Marius Dorobantu, comments: “During my time at Coventry University, my life has changed in countless positive ways. I feel my course has enriched me with experiences that will make a great difference to my future.” Olumayowa Adekoya, an MSc Engineering Business Management student who kick started his own photography business, said: “The thing I enjoyed the most about my course are the case studies, as I could reflect on my past professional experiences. It gave me a deeper understanding of how to improve and broaden my business management knowledge.” Students on all courses benefit from Coventry’s five-star QS Stars University Ratings, including Employability, Teaching, and Facilities.<img loading="lazy" class="wp-image-1666458 aligncenter lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unnamed-63.png" alt="" width="600" height="399" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unnamed-63.png 451w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unnamed-63-320x213.jpg 320w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" />  Study options for everyone Alongside its full-time on campus offering, Coventry University offers part-time, fast track, online and blended study options, and on some courses, pay-as-you-go options are also available. Are you interested in business, fashion, finance, marketing, or hospitality? Coventry University London offers a range of these courses, inclusive of an internship or work placement credit. Coventry University Online is also open to you this May and September. There are no fixed timetables and dozens of courses to pick from, which was one of the reasons Coventry was awarded first place in the world for Massive Online Open Courses (MoocLab’s World University Rankings by MOOC Performance 2021). Need to boost your qualifications to gain entry onto a Coventry University course? The university offers high-quality Foundation, International Year One and Pre-Masters study routes if you don’t meet the requirements for direct entry. Comprehensive student support Alongside Coventry University’s strong academic offering, following your enrolment, you’ll be introduced to your personal Success Coach and Academic Tutor to support your personal and academic journey. As your life coach, Success Coaches are there to help you discover what you really want and how to achieve it. They will give you the support you need to make the most of your course, and all that university life offers. Your Academic Personal Tutor will be your go-to expert about everything to do with your course, offering an additional layer of support alongside your lecturers. They can help you apply for internships and be your first professional contact from the industry in your network. <img loading="lazy" class="wp-image-1666457 aligncenter lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unnamed-64.png" alt="" width="600" height="399" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unnamed-64.png 451w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unnamed-64-320x213.jpg 320w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /> Discover your future The Coventry University application process is straightforward, with the International Student Support Team offering immediate and highly accessible support to applicants of all languages. Olumayowa Adekoya, an Engineering Business Management postgraduate, said: “The Coventry University admissions team is the most engaging among the universities I have applied for, and their admission process is also seamless.” Begin your academic journey with the inspiring and sector-leading institution. Here’s how you can find out more about Coventry University, Coventry University London or Coventry University Online: